OL,3,CAmerican professor falls in love with
OL,4,CWales and learns to speak Welsh
OL,6,FAn American professor who fell in love
OL,7,Fwith Wales and learned to speak Welsh
OL,8,Fhas created a programme for State-side
OL,9,Fstudents to study and work in Cardiff.
OL,11,FMatthew Jones, a professor with the
OL,12,FUniversity of Florida, first fell in
OL,13,Flove with the history of Wales during
OL,14,Fhis studies in 2015 and committed to
OL,15,Flearn a few words.
OL,17,FBut now he has gone much further than
OL,18,Fthat and Matthew is now bringing
OL,19,Fgroups of students to Cardiff
OL,20,FUniversity throughout the summer.
