OL,3,CAmerican professor falls in love with
OL,4,CWales and learns to speak Welsh
OL,6,FMr Jones says he was unaware of the
OL,7,FWelsh language until he "stumbled
OL,8,Facross it" while studying British
OL,9,FLiterature.
OL,11,F"I was studying British Literature,
OL,12,Fand I came across the work of Iolo
OL,13,FMorganwg," he said. "I had never seen
OL,14,Fthe Welsh language before, and I felt
OL,15,Fthat I had to learn more about the
OL,16,Flanguage in order to understand the
OL,17,Fearly literature better.
