OL,3,CAmerican professor falls in love with
OL,4,CWales and learns to speak Welsh
OL,6,F"After I'd done a bit of research, I
OL,7,Frealised that Welsh is a living
OL,8,Flanguage, still spoken in Wales today,
OL,9,Fand I decided I needed to learn some
OL,10,FWelsh."
OL,12,FThat led to Mr Jones coming to Cardiff
OL,13,FUniversity to study a master's degree
OL,14,Ffor a year in 2015, and he also had
OL,15,FWelsh lessons.
OL,17,FHe says he immersed himself in the
OL,18,FWelsh culture of the capital city, and
OL,19,Fby the time he left he could speak
OL,20,FWelsh.
