OL,3,CAmerican professor falls in love with
OL,4,CWales and learns to speak Welsh
OL,6,F"I still tell people that the Welsh
OL,7,Flanguage saved my life in some way. I
OL,8,Ffound direction in my life for the
OL,9,Ffirst time at the age of 28."
OL,11,FNow, he's working to spread the love
OL,12,Fof Wales to others.
OL,14,FThe aim of his summer course is to
OL,15,Fgive the students an opportunity to
OL,16,Fcome to Wales to get work experience,
OL,17,Flearn about the country, its history,
OL,18,Fculture and also the language.
