OL,6,FMr Jones has been working with Cardiff
OL,7,FUniversity's Law School, some of the
OL,8,Fcity's law firms and the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment, to shape the programme,
OL,10,Fwhich is now in its second year.
OL,12,FHe said: "The programme gives students
OL,13,Fenough time to enjoy the hustle and
OL,14,Fbustle of Cardiff and get a taste of
OL,15,Fthe workplace.
